ChangeList.Description: Removed the following methods for retrieving custom authentication extension objects: `GET /identity/authenticationEventListeners/{listenerId}/microsoft.graph.onAttributeCollectionStartListener/handler/microsoft.graph.onAttributeCollectionStartCustomExtensionHandler/customExtension`, `GET /identity/authenticationEventListeners/{listenerId}/microsoft.graph.onAttributeCollectionSubmitListener/handler/microsoft.graph.onAttributeCollectionSubmitCustomExtensionHandler/customExtension` , `GET /identity/authenticationEventListeners/{listenerId}/microsoft.graph.OnEmailOtpSendListener/handler/microsoft.graph.OnOtpSendCustomExtensionHandler/customExtension`. Use the [GET /identity/customAuthenticationExtensions/{customAuthenticationExtensionId}](https://learn.microsoft.com/en-us/graph/api/customauthenticationextension-get?view=graph-rest-beta) operation instead.

Removed the following methods for updating custom authentication extension objects: `PUT /identity/authenticationEventListeners/{listenerId}/microsoft.graph.onAttributeCollectionStartListener/handler/microsoft.graph.onAttributeCollectionStartCustomExtensionHandler/customExtension/$ref` , `PUT /identity/authenticationEventListeners/{listenerId}/microsoft.graph.onAttributeCollectionSubmitListener/handler/microsoft.graph.onAttributeCollectionSubmitCustomExtensionHandler/customExtension/$ref` , `PUT /identity/authenticationEventListeners/{listenerId}/microsoft.graph.onEmailOtpSendListener/handler/microsoft.graph.onOtpSendCustomExtensionHandler/customExtension/$ref`. Use the [PATCH /identity/customAuthenticationExtensions/{customAuthenticationExtensionId}](https://learn.microsoft.com/en-us/graph/api/customauthenticationextension-update?view=graph-rest-beta) operation instead.
Added the **behaviorOnError** property to the [customAuthenticationExtension](https://learn.microsoft.com/en-us/graph/api/resources/customAuthenticationExtension?view=graph-rest-beta) resource.

Added the `onAttributeCollectionStart` property to the [externalUsersSelfServiceSignUpEventsFlow](https://learn.microsoft.com/en-us/graph/api/resources/externalUsersSelfServiceSignUpEventsFlow?view=graph-rest-beta) resource.

Added the `onAttributeCollectionSubmit` property to the [externalUsersSelfServiceSignUpEventsFlow](https://learn.microsoft.com/en-us/graph/api/resources/externalUsersSelfServiceSignUpEventsFlow?view=graph-rest-beta) resource.
Added the **authenticationEventsFlows** relationship to the [identityContainer](https://learn.microsoft.com/en-us/graph/api/resources/identityContainer?view=graph-rest-1.0) resource.

Added the [authenticationEventsFlow](https://learn.microsoft.com/en-us/graph/api/resources/authenticationEventsFlow?view=graph-rest-1.0) resource and its associated methods. Use this resource and its derived types and API operations to manage user flows in Microsoft Entra External ID in external tenants.
Added the **authenticationEventListeners** relationship to the [identityContainer](https://learn.microsoft.com/en-us/graph/api/resources/identityContainer?view=graph-rest-beta) resource.
Added the **customAuthenticationExtensions** relationship to the [identityContainer](https://learn.microsoft.com/en-us/graph/api/resources/identityContainer?view=graph-rest-beta) resource.

Added the [customAuthenticationExtension](https://learn.microsoft.com/en-us/graph/api/resources/customAuthenticationExtension?view=graph-rest-beta) resource. Use this resource and its associated methods to manage configurations to systems that are external to Azure AD, such as databases and APIs. The data from these external systems can be used to customize the Azure AD authentication experience for users.

Added the [authenticationEventListener](https://learn.microsoft.com/en-us/graph/api/resources/authenticationEventListener?view=graph-rest-beta) resource. Use this resource and its associated methods to manage the listeners and handlers that trigger the execution of custom logic during the Azure AD authentication experience

Added the [validateAuthenticationConfiguration](https://learn.microsoft.com/en-us/graph/api/customauthenticationextension-validateauthenticationconfiguration?view=graph-rest-beta) method to the resource.

Added the [validateAuthenticationConfiguration](https://learn.microsoft.com/en-us/graph/api/customauthenticationextension-validateauthenticationconfiguration?view=graph-rest-beta) method to the [customAuthenticationExtensions](https://learn.microsoft.com/en-us/graph/api/resources/identityContainer?view=graph-rest-beta) resource.
Added the **authenticationEventsFlows** relationship to the [identityContainer](https://learn.microsoft.com/en-us/graph/api/resources/identityContainer?view=graph-rest-beta) resource.
Added the **authenticationEventListeners** relationship to the [identityContainer](https://learn.microsoft.com/en-us/graph/api/resources/identityContainer?view=graph-rest-1.0) resource.
Added the **customAuthenticationExtensions** relationship to the [identityContainer](https://learn.microsoft.com/en-us/graph/api/resources/identityContainer?view=graph-rest-1.0) resource.

Added the [validateAuthenticationConfiguration](https://learn.microsoft.com/en-us/graph/api/customAuthenticationExtension-validateAuthenticationConfiguration?view=graph-rest-1.0) method to the [customAuthenticationExtension](https://learn.microsoft.com/en-us/graph/api/resources/customAuthenticationExtension?view=graph-rest-1.0) resource.

Added the [validateAuthenticationConfiguration](https://learn.microsoft.com/en-us/graph/api/customAuthenticationExtension-validateAuthenticationConfiguration?view=graph-rest-1.0) method to the [customAuthenticationExtension](https://learn.microsoft.com/en-us/graph/api/resources/customAuthenticationExtension?view=graph-rest-1.0) resource.
Added the **status** property to the [trustFrameworkKey](https://learn.microsoft.com/en-us/graph/api/resources/trustFrameworkKey?view=graph-rest-beta) resource.
Added the **keys_v2** relationship to the [trustFrameworkKeySet](https://learn.microsoft.com/en-us/graph/api/resources/trustFrameworkKeySet?view=graph-rest-beta) resource.
Added the [trustFrameworkKey_v2](https://learn.microsoft.com/en-us/graph/api/resources/trustFrameworkKey_v2?view=graph-rest-beta) resource and its associated methods.
